data.description: Welcome to this brand new 1.5-story home, on a spacious lot backing to common ground & woods with a walking trail that leads you to all that O'Day Park has to offer! Designed with meticulous attention to detail, it is sure to impress. The expansive windows throughout the home flood each room with natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere for any occasion. The main floor master suite provides a haven of relaxation with the ensuite bath featuring dual vanities, large soaking tub, spacious walk-in shower with seat and dual shower heads, and oversized walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find 3 additional bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a loft space that could be flexible and serve as an office, a kids' play area, or entertainment room. The full basement walks out to the expansive backyard, where you can sit and watch all the wildlife passing through O'Day Park. The subdivision offers a clubhouse with entertaining space, workout gym, inground pool, and more! Make your appointment today!
